Jenny Beck https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jenny_Beck 0 Jennifer "Jenny" Beck (born August 3, 1974 in Los Angeles, California) is an American actress best known for playing a young Elizabeth on V: The Final Battle and V: The Series (episode 1). Her other well-known television role was on Paradise as Claire Carroll. She received three consecutive Young Artist Award nominations, 1989 to 1991, Best Young Actress Starring in a Television Series, for her role in Paradise. She had roles in three feature films, Tightrope (1984), The Canterville Ghost (1985) and Troll (1986).
